    <item>
      <title>马尼拉唐人街发生火灾，造成至少 11 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-02/a-fire-sweeps-through-a-building-in-manila-s-chinatown-killing-at-least-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尼拉，菲律宾（美联社）——警方称，周五马尼拉繁忙的唐人街一栋小型建筑发生火灾，造成至少 11 人死亡，并补充说正在调查起火原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-02/a-fire-sweeps-through-a-building-in-manila-s-chinatown-killing-at-least-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
