      <title>拜登向内塔尼亚胡承诺“新的美国防御性军事部署”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列面临报复暗杀哈马斯和真主党领导人的新威胁之际，美国总统乔·拜登向本杰明·内塔尼亚胡承诺“新的美国防御性军事部署”，但他也敦促以色列领导人推进停火努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
